{
  "texts": [
    "On the QUAD-Dataset, the T5-Large outperforms ChatGPT significantly.",
    "RLHF may lead to unexpected phenomena.",
    "The experimental results indicate that ChatGPT performs poorly in detecting hate speech, irony, and offensive language.",
    "Even compared to text-003, which performs similarly well in many other tasks, ChatGPT's performance is notably worse in these three tasks.",
    "This finding highlights the necessity for further research and improvement in these domains, as it suggests that ChatGPT's RLHF process excessively aligns with human biases and preferences."
  ]
}